cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

The paper deals with computer vision and robotics, specifically the task of 6D pose estimation of texture-less objects. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The dataset and the task also involve machine learning, which makes cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely category. The use of synchronized sensors and the focus on robotics make cs.RO (Robotics) a possible category as well. The paper also mentions the need for improving the state of the art in 6D object pose estimation, which suggests a focus on artificial intelligence and optimization, making cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) a possible category. Finally, the paper involves 3D modeling and geometry, which could make cs.GR (Graphics) a possible category.
